    group: "20 MAD per person (‚Ç¨2)"
  },
  highlights: [
    "17th-century palace with stunning architecture",
    "Panoramic views of the Strait of Gibraltar",
    "Extensive collection of Moroccan ceramics",
    "Ancient Roman mosaics from Volubilis",
